result.name: San Kee Congee

reviews.text: Delicious local eatery that offers all traditional items of Cantonese breakfast, fast  and efficent service. If you can't speak Chinese, just point at what is being cooked at the open kitchen. They start at 0600 AM. Given the current super high inflation on rents in the Hung Hom area, one may wonder how much longer they will survive. It's a must-try.
Awesome food here.. normal local food price.. very smooth delicious porridge, lady boss is extremely friendly as well and not impatient at all
Very tasty
